{ [#] }
1... Bxf3! (1... Qxh4?? 2. Nxh4 $18) (1... Rg8? 2. Ng5 { and Black's
attack is stopped }) 2. Qxb4 (2. gxf3? { loses immediate after } 2... Rg8+ 3. Kh1 Qxh4#) 2... Rg8 3. g3 Rg4! { This forcing move is attacking White's queen and
is enabling Black to play Qxh4 next. } 4. Qc5 Qxh4! { the shortest path to a
checkmate } (4... Rxh4 { wins the game as well } 5. Qxc6+ Kf8 6. gxh4 Qxh4 7. Qc5+ Kg7 { followed by Qh1# }) 5. Qxc6+ Kf8 6. Qa8+ Kg7 { followed by Qh1# } 0-1


